@startuml

Digital Watch State Diagram

state Idle
Idle --> AdjustTime : Button Pressed

state AdjustTime
AdjustTime --> HourAdjust : Button Pressed (Hour)
AdjustTime --> MinuteAdjust : Button Pressed (Minute)
AdjustTime --> AlarmHourAdjust : Button Pressed (Alarm Hour)
AdjustTime --> AlarmMinuteAdjust : Button Pressed (Alarm Minute)

state HourAdjust
HourAdjust --> IncreaseHour : Button Pressed (Increase)
HourAdjust --> DecreaseHour : Button Pressed (Decrease)

state MinuteAdjust
MinuteAdjust --> IncreaseMinute : Button Pressed (Increase)
MinuteAdjust --> DecreaseMinute : Button Pressed (Decrease)

state AlarmHourAdjust
AlarmHourAdjust --> IncreaseAlarmHour : Button Pressed (Increase)
AlarmHourAdjust --> DecreaseAlarmHour : Button Pressed (Decrease)

state AlarmMinuteAdjust
AlarmMinuteAdjust --> IncreaseAlarmMinute : Button Pressed (Increase)
AlarmMinuteAdjust --> DecreaseAlarmMinute : Button Pressed (Decrease)

state OnAlarm
OnAlarm --> RingAlarm : Current Time Matches Alarm Time
OnAlarm --> StopAlarm : Specific Button Pressed

state OffAlarm
OffAlarm --> OnAlarm : Alarm Toggled On

state LightControl
LightControl --> LightOn : Button Pressed (Light)
LightControl --> LightOff : Button Released (Light)

@enduml
